{"tid":324792,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Body Check要我自己帶啲屎去，點裝去好？","createTime":"2017-07-16T16:43:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T18:09:41.000Z","uid":77194,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9559043d97b10e6577ae04a87a1da180c7a9a89c","tid":324792,"uid":77194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T16:43:22.000Z","msg":"我下個月由part time轉full time<br />\n公司要我簽約前去body check<br />\n淨係比咗個膠樽仔我<br />\n叫我上去check嗰陣帶埋啲大便樣本上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗緊點樣裝啲屎入個膠樽好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有同事叫我痾係報紙上面再𢳂入個樽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為啲屎唔可以掂到任何野（姐係唔可以普通痾屎咁 啲屎唔可以掂到咸水）<br />\n咁就碌柒啦 無啦啦要我玩屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋我要搭半個鐘地鐵先去到旺角間診所<br />\n要拎住啲屎周圍走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/17/003640_7f1d91ce8b5376ae905dc6a55ad4b020.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F17%2F003640_7f1d91ce8b5376ae905dc6a55ad4b020.jpg&h=f4c2b74e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee26d03a10e58136866b798378efb48d44664220","tid":324792,"uid":68553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T16:46:59.000Z","msg":"去到間診所先屙"},{"pid":"ee4b5b4a81157bc1ce16013182ebd47d913ae69e","tid":324792,"uid":71609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T16:47:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去到間診所先屙</blockquote><br />\n完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c85cd3e09c335f95709f93972294b8cdd94365cf","tid":324792,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T16:48:54.000Z","msg":